0.0.2
-----
1. Wait for 5 seconds for URL to load. If an invalid server address is entered
   then this will timeout.
2. If no server configured, attempt to auto-discover and use first server found.
3. Add button in settings dialog to discover server.
4. If click on 'discovef server' and another server that is not the current one
   is found, then the server is changed to the first new one.

